for tc in range(int(input())):
    n = int(input())
    arr = list(map(int, input().split()))
    maxdiff = 0
    maxgoal = [arr[-1]] * n
    for i in range(n - 2, -1, -1):
        maxgoal[i] = max(arr[i], maxgoal[i + 1])
        maxdiff = max(maxdiff, maxgoal[i] - arr[i])
    print(maxdiff if maxdiff else 'UNFIT')

t = int(input())
for i in range(0, t):
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    netmax = 0
    mini = a[0]
    for x in a:
        netmax = max(netmax, x - mini)
        mini = min(mini, x)
    print(netmax if netmax > 0 else 'UNFIT')

for _ in range(int(input())):
    n = int(input())
    gi = list(map(int, input().split()))
    start = gi[0]
    result = 0
    i = 0
    while i < n - 1:
        if gi[i + 1] < gi[i]:
            start = min(start, gi[i + 1])
            i += 1
        else:
            result = max(result, gi[i + 1] - start)
            i += 1
    print('UNFIT') if result == 0 else print(result)

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    n = int(input())
    l = list(map(int, input().split()))
    minV = l[0]
    ans = -1
    for i in l:
        ans = max(ans, i - minV)
        minV = min(minV, i)
    if ans <= 0:
        print('UNFIT')
        continue
    print(ans)

T = int(input())
for x in range(T):
    N = int(input())
    goals = list(map(int, input().split()))
    b = list()
    c = list()
    b.append(goals[0])
    c.append(goals[N - 1])
    ele = goals[0]
    for i in range(1, N):
        ele = min(goals[i], ele)
        b.append(ele)
    ele = goals[N - 1]
    for i in range(2, N + 1):
        ele = max(goals[N - i], ele)
        c.append(ele)
    ele = 0
    for i in range(N):
        ele = max(ele, c[i] - b[N - 1 - i])
    if ele == 0:
        print('UNFIT')
    else:
        print(ele)

t = int(input())
while t:
    t -= 1
    n = int(input())
    li = list(map(int, input().split()))
    (mini, maxi) = (li[0], li[0])
    res = 0
    for i in range(1, n):
        maxi = max(maxi, li[i])
        if mini > li[i]:
            mini = li[i]
            maxi = 0
        res = max(res, maxi - mini)
    if res == 0:
        print('UNFIT')
    else:
        print(res)
